WEBVTT

01:15.800 --> 01:17.500
你得想想办法 我弟弟是无辜的
You got do something,my brother is innocent.

01:17.660 --> 01:18.700
他可是美国公民啊
He's an American citizen.

01:18.760 --> 01:20.300
对此我也无能为力
Look,there's nothing I can do about that.

01:20.360 --> 01:20.960
你当然能
Of course there is

01:20.990 --> 01:21.900
再去犯罪现场看看 定能证实清白
back at the crime scene,that'll prove

01:21.960 --> 01:23.130
你看 我不过是个夜间办事员而已
Look,I'm a night clerk,okay?

01:23.200 --> 01:24.460
你若真想解决问题
If you want someone who can really do something,

01:24.530 --> 01:25.700
最好等领事来
you're gonna have to wait for the consul

01:25.760 --> 01:27.960
他早上才上班
he gets in in the morning.

01:28.030 --> 01:29.730
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

01:30.860 --> 01:32.560
那我自己来搞定
That ain't gonna cut it.

01:33.800 --> 01:34.900
你兄弟
Your brother,

01:34.960 --> 01:36.960
关在哪个监狱?
where do they have him incarcerated?

01:37.030 --> 01:38.060
索纳监狱
Sona.

01:39.530 --> 01:40.960
怎么了?
What?

01:42.960 --> 01:45.400
那里关的都是最穷凶极恶的罪犯
The worst of the worst are there,

01:45.460 --> 01:47.930
别的监狱都不收
men no other prison will take.

01:53.860 --> 01:56.400
一年前 他们野蛮暴动过
They rioted so badly a year ago,

01:56.460 --> 01:58.100
守卫都撤了出来
the guards pulled out,

01:58.160 --> 02:00.030
留下他们自生自灭
just left them to themselves.

02:00.100 --> 02:03.960
成千上万的小偷 强奸犯 杀人犯
A thousand thieves,rapists,murderers.

02:13.860 --> 02:16.300
政府干脆退避三舍
The government just stays back,

02:16.360 --> 02:17.430
保持他们的原样
keeps the perimeter.

02:27.530 --> 02:30.900
都说那是"单行道"
To them,Sona's a one-way street.

02:30.960 --> 02:33.400
只有进
What goes in

02:33.460 --> 02:35.330
没有出
never comes out

02:35.400 --> 02:37.360
除非死了
unless it's dead.

