我们要求将他转移至更
and we need him moved to a facility that's a little

03:33.830 --> 03:34.870
适合的机构
more moderate.

03:34.930 --> 03:36.470
行吗?
All right?

03:36.530 --> 03:38.070
谢谢你
Thank you.

03:38.130 --> 03:39.670
是这样的 好消息是
All right,the good news is as of yesterday

03:39.730 --> 03:40.870
从昨天起 你重获自由了
you're a free man.

03:40.930 --> 03:42.470
你无需再担心什么了
You got nothing to worry about.

03:42.530 --> 03:43.700
我担心我弟弟
Just my brother.

03:43.770 --> 03:46.270
好吧 你们俩的事迹传得很神
Right. Well,that's a heck of a story,you two.

03:46.330 --> 03:48.300
消息甚至传到了这
That made the news even down here.

03:48.370 --> 03:50.400
我听说你还有个儿子
And I understand you have a son as well?

03:50.470 --> 03:52.330
-没错 -叫LJ 小林肯?
-Yeah. Uh-huh. -LJ Lincoln Jr.?

03:52.400 --> 03:53.670
他得知你恢复清白身 一定很兴奋
He must be ecstatic about your exoneration.

03:53.730 --> 03:55.730
还没联系上他
Still trying to reach him.

03:55.800 --> 03:57.970
你可以告诉我们他在哪里
Well,hey,tell us where he is.

03:58.030 --> 03:59.000
-我们派人去 -我自己能搞定
-We'll send -Let me handle that.

03:59.070 --> 04:01.130
让我们还是先关注迈克吧
Let's just focus on Michael.

04:01.200 --> 04:03.530
好的 好消息是
Okay,well,good news is is that much

04:03.600 --> 04:06.130
你所说的一切与犯罪现场吻合
of what you're saying is checking out at the crime scene.

04:06.200 --> 04:08.600
被害人的确有一把特工专用左轮手枪
The victim did have a service revolver

04:08.670 --> 04:10.400
上面刻有政府编号
with U.S. government numbers on it.

04:10.470 --> 04:12.830
凶器既然已经发现
And if a weapon was found,then that lends

04:12.900 --> 04:15.570
那么对自卫一说提供了有利物证
real credence to self-defense as a motive.

04:15.630 --> 04:16.270
很好
Great.

04:16.330 --> 04:18.770
他们有没有发现别的?
They,uh,find anything else?

04:18.830 --> 04:20.700
-比如说哪方面? -包
-Like what? -A bag.

04:20.770 --> 04:21.830
里面有什么?
What was in it?

04:21.900 --> 04:23.700
有些钱吧
A little money.

04:23.770 --> 04:24.830
没有发现 不好意思
No,sorry.

04:24.900 --> 04:25.930
没关系
Of course they didn't.

04:26.000 --> 04:27.500
不管发生什么情况
Yeah,well,whatever the case,

04:27.570 --> 04:28.930
对于你兄弟而言
regarding your brother,I have managed

04:29.000 --> 04:30.500
我都会设法做些改变
to make a little headway.

04:30.570 --> 04:31.730
我已作出了安排
I arranged for a transfer

04:31.800 --> 04:33.130
把你兄弟转移到别的地方
for your brother to another facility,

04:33.200 --> 04:34.270
明天就能生效
effective tomorrow.

04:34.330 --> 04:35.430
那里要安全
It's a lot safer,

04:35.500 --> 04:37.330
-干净得多 -很好
-it's a lot cleaner. -Great.

04:37.400 --> 04:40.830
如我所想那样 会有足够的证据
And if this is stacking up like I think it is,

04:40.900 --> 04:43.300
我有十足的把握 所有控告都会撤销
I'd be pretty confident the charges will be dropped.

04:43.370 --> 04:45.300
他会无罪释放?
He'd be free?

04:45.370 --> 04:47.600
可能还要面对美国方面的指控
Well,he'd still face charges in the U.S.

04:47.670 --> 04:49.670
但那是出狱以后的事了?
But out of there?

04:49.830 --> 04:50.870
没错
Yes.

05:41.370 --> 05:43.670
这里有 有集体食堂吗?
Is there is there a mess hall here?

05:43.730 --> 05:45.300
集体食堂?
Mess hall?

05:45.370 --> 05:47.370
还要点水
And some water.

05:47.430 --> 05:48.470
求求你 我快渴死了
I'm dying of thirst. Please.

05:48.530 --> 05:50.800
求求你了
Please.

05:51.160 --> 05:52.930
这里倒是有些水
There's some water.

05:56.930 --> 05:58.070
去死吧
Bite me.

06:00.370 --> 06:01.330
你说什么?
What'd you say?

06:01.400 --> 06:02.530
我什么也没说
I didn't say nothing.

06:05.500 --> 06:07.730
喝了它
Drink it.

06:07.800 --> 06:08.770
听见没有
You hear me?

06:08.830 --> 06:10.970
喝了它
Drink

06:28.230 --> 06:31.500
伙计 这里就是这样的
Hey,get used to it,man.

06:31.570 --> 06:34.270
我也好几天没吃东西了
I haven't eaten for days.

06:34.330 --> 06:36.570
起来
Come on.

07:38.030 --> 07:39.470
你还好吧?
How are you doing?

07:39.530 --> 07:40.900
阿历克斯 你想怎样?
What do you want,Alex?

07:40.970 --> 07:44.530
你太聪敏了 居然想出在船上放毒品栽赃
You're so clever like planting the drugs on the boat.

07:44.600 --> 07:45.700
这太嘲讽了
That's a big irony.

07:45.770 --> 07:47.800
关在监狱里的罗曼
Lawman in jail.

07:47.870 --> 07:49.700
你现在罪有应得了
You are exactly where you belong.

07:49.770 --> 07:50.900
不 这就是你错误的地方
No,that's where you're wrong.

07:50.970 --> 07:52.430
我需要你的帮助
And that's where you're gonna help me.

07:52.500 --> 07:53.900
这几天我就要接受庭审了
I will have a court date one of these days,

07:53.970 --> 07:55.300
你到时也会出庭
and you will be there on the stand.

07:55.370 --> 07:57.670
你会告诉大家事实你计划了这一切
And you will tell the truth that you planted this

07:57.730 --> 08:00.330
你设计栽赃 我就可以回家了
and you set this up,and I'm gonna go home.

08:00.400 --> 08:03.930
这太嘲讽了 我对天发誓是你设的局
That's funny,I could have sworn you set this up.

08:06.130 --> 08:08.530
我设的局? 我被关在这儿
I set this up? I'm in here.

08:08.600 --> 08:10.030
幕后者到底对我有何企图?
What does the Company want with me?

08:10.100 --> 08:11.170
为什么挑选巴拿马?
Why Panama?

08:11.230 --> 08:13.500
你觉得我这样子像知道这一切吗?
What,you think I know what they wanted?

08:13.570 --> 08:16.130
我受他们控制
They had me.

08:16.200 --> 08:17.800
听命于他们
I did what they asked me to do

08:17.870 --> 08:19.630
在巴拿马逮捕你
arrest you in Panama

08:19.700 --> 08:21.000
并移送回来
hand you over.

08:21.070 --> 08:22.630
这 这一切
That's it. That's,that's

08:25.930 --> 08:28.330
这一切现在听来都是旧事了
That's old news,huh?

08:28.400 --> 08:30.670
从今天开始 我们重新回归正途
This is the first day of the rest of our lives.

08:30.730 --> 08:32.770
不如我们联手 怎样?
How about we work together,you know?

08:32.830 --> 08:34.530
互相帮助 一起逃出去
Help each other out.

08:34.600 --> 08:36.570
但我每次看到你
Except every time I look at you,

08:36.630 --> 08:39.230
就想起那个杀了我父亲的凶手
all I can see is the man who killed my father.

08:41.200 --> 08:42.570
你自谋生路吧
You're on your own.

08:52.790 --> 08:55.570
把我老公带出来
My husband Bring him out

08:55.660 --> 08:57.070
我知道他昨天被杀了
I know he was killed last night

08:57.270 --> 08:58.350
有人给我打电话了
Someone called

08:58.930 --> 09:01.280
把我老公带出来
Bring my husbang out now

09:08.000 --> 09:08.790
小心点
Be careful.

09:15.000 --> 09:17.100
在这里登记 进去后
Sign here to say that once inside,

09:17.170 --> 09:18.570
根据我国法律 就你自己负责了
you're on your own by the law,

09:18.630 --> 09:20.970
任何意外都不受军方或者法律保护
that you're not protected by the military in case of an assault.

09:21.030 --> 09:23.670
任何协助在押犯逃跑的企图
And any attempt to assist an inmate trying to escape

09:23.730 --> 09:25.200
都以死罪论处
will be met with a lethal response.

09:25.270 --> 09:26.900
想都没有想过
Wouldn't dream of it.

09:42.600 --> 09:44.770
怎样
So

09:44.830 --> 09:46.430
不怎样
So

09:46.500 --> 09:49.570
感觉我站错边了
Feel like I'm on the wrong side.

09:49.630 --> 09:51.600
你在你该在的地方
You're on the right side.

09:51.670 --> 09:52.700
可你不在
You're not.

09:52.770 --> 09:54.570
要帮我越狱?
Gonna break me out?

09:54.630 --> 09:57.100
一路亡命太辛苦了
Too tiring. All that running.

09:57.170 --> 09:59.630
或许你已经把逃亡靴给丢了
Yeah,well,maybe you should have lost the cowboy boots.

09:59.700 --> 10:02.200
你害怕了?
You scared?

10:04.470 --> 10:07.800
-我现在就要把你救出来 -林肯
-I'm getting you out of here,man. -Linc.

10:07.870 --> 10:09.700
听着 上头准备把你转移到安全的地方
Listen,the Consulate's arranged to transfer you to a

10:09.770 --> 10:12.800
大约一个月后 你就有重获自由的机会
safer facility until the trial which is about a month.

10:12.970 --> 10:16.070
他们说你有很大机会无罪释放
They say you got a good shot of walking out of here a free man.

10:16.130 --> 10:17.170
什么时候转移?
When's the transfer?

10:17.230 --> 10:18.470
明天
Tomorrow.

10:18.530 --> 10:21.830
再等等 多等一天
Just just hold on,man,one more day.

10:21.900 --> 10:24.070
希望你能快点找到她的消息
You know,I keep waiting for you to mention a certain someone.

10:26.730 --> 10:29.100
兄弟 我不知道她在哪
I don't know where she is,man.

10:29.170 --> 10:30.370
你得找到她
Well,you got to find her.

10:30.430 --> 10:31.500
我会的
I will.

10:31.570 --> 10:36.270
林肯 这对我很重要
She's important to me,Linc.

10:36.330 --> 10:39.400
要是莎拉发生了什么事
If anything happens to Sara

10:41.770 --> 10:44.670
一切都会好的 兄弟
It's going to be fine,man.

10:44.730 --> 10:47.630
我保证
I promise.

10:47.700 --> 10:51.630
明天见
I'll see you tomorrow.

10:51.700 --> 10:53.970
好吗?
All right?

11:15.570 --> 11:16.970
你是美国人 对吧?
American,right?

11:17.030 --> 11:18.770
我热爱美国
I love America.

11:18.830 --> 11:22.030
NBA 特雷西·麦迪的神奇表现
NBA. Tracy McGrady shooting the ball in the hoop from downtown.

11:22.100 --> 11:23.900
不管你想推销什么 我都不感兴趣
Whatever you're selling,I'm not buying.

11:23.970 --> 11:25.600
推销?
Selling?

11:25.670 --> 11:27.500
我只是想跟你说说篮球
I just want to talk basketball.

11:27.570 --> 11:28.730
你喜欢哪个球队?
Who's your team?

11:32.270 --> 11:33.370
小子 跟我们走
Let's go,blanco.

11:33.430 --> 11:34.370
带你熟悉下环境
Orientation.

11:34.430 --> 11:35.400
我没兴趣
I'm not interested.

11:35.470 --> 11:37.300
没你选的份
It's not for you to decide.

11:45.860 --> 11:48.370
守卫说我得在15分钟后离开
Guards say I have to be out in 15 minutes.

11:56.230 --> 11:57.430
把他们带进来
Bring them in.

12:15.300 --> 12:17.900
我真希望他们没让你们吃什么苦头
Well,I hope they haven't been treating you too poorly.

12:17.970 --> 12:20.100
如果有的话 我应该有所耳闻了
I should hear of it if you have.

12:20.170 --> 12:23.300
我想你们能看出这地方与众不同
I think as you can tell,Sona is unlike any other place in the world.

12:23.370 --> 12:26.400
那帮守卫去年仓皇而逃
Huh? Since the riots of last year,they left us here to rot.

12:26.470 --> 12:28.000
他们认为我们会内耗而亡
They figured we would just destroy ourselves,

12:28.070 --> 12:29.800
恰恰相反 我们队伍更壮大了
but instead,we've thrived.

12:29.870 --> 12:32.430
借助于巴拿马运河
With the canal,Panama is now

12:32.500 --> 12:34.230
巴拿马现在成了全球罪犯的孵化基地
a breeding ground for international crime.

12:34.300 --> 12:37.230
我们这的人来自27个不同国家
27 different nationalities we have here.

12:37.300 --> 12:39.830
但不是一个帮派的
But not one gang.

12:39.900 --> 12:42.370
没有一起种族歧视案例
Not one racially-motivated incident.

12:43.970 --> 12:46.300
这都归功于我
It's just me.

12:46.370 --> 12:49.600
平等主义
Egalitarianism

12:49.670 --> 12:51.900
这是我的信仰
I believe is the word.

12:51.970 --> 12:54.400
你不同意吗?
Huh? Did I get that right?

12:54.470 --> 12:56.170
你说是就是了
Right as rain.

12:57.700 --> 12:59.830
操练一下果然长进了
That's what practice does for you.

12:59.900 --> 13:04.270
你们有什么要向我汇报的吗?
Now,is there anything you want to tell me?

13:04.330 --> 13:08.730
我想知道你们被关进来的原因
Any history that you bring to this place that I should know about?

13:16.630 --> 13:19.630
我想你没说实话
I don't think you're quite telling me the truth,

13:19.700 --> 13:21.500
斯科菲尔德先生
Mr. Scofield.

13:21.570 --> 13:23.470
我们已经听到了风声 老兄
We get the news,man.

13:23.530 --> 13:28.170
你在CNN上俨然是个超级明星了
You were quite the superstar on CNN.

13:28.230 --> 13:29.570
救出了你哥后
Man breaks brother out

13:29.630 --> 13:31.330
然后逃亡到巴拿马
and flees to Panama.

13:33.170 --> 13:35.430
但在这你可行不通了
But you're not a superstar here

13:35.500 --> 13:36.600
你没意识到这点吗?
You realize that,don't you?

13:36.670 --> 13:38.130
我不想在起什么波澜
I'm not going to make waves.

13:40.170 --> 13:41.500
凭你的能耐也办不到
It wouldn't be within your power.

13:48.270 --> 13:51.270
我也听说过你们俩
I heard about the two of you.

13:51.330 --> 13:52.570
你们今天闯祸了
You two in the hall today.

13:52.630 --> 13:54.700
但你俩如果想解决问题的话
Now,if you would like to sort your problems out,

13:54.770 --> 13:56.330
方法很简单
it's very simple here.

13:59.070 --> 14:02.630
两人之间意见不同
A man has a beef with another,he makes his problem known.

14:04.270 --> 14:06.230
就直接用男人的方式解决问题
And then we deal with it directly

14:06.300 --> 14:09.400
就在那里
as men over there.

14:09.470 --> 14:12.470
没那个必要
Won't be necessary.

14:22.600 --> 14:25.470
你一直那样发抖的吗
You always shake like that?

14:27.130 --> 14:29.170
还是仅仅出于对某人的畏惧
Or just when you're scared of someone?

14:39.170 --> 14:40.170
你呢?
What about you?

14:41.170 --> 14:42.570
老大 不要伤害我
Dont hurt me man.

14:43.570 --> 14:44.570
我不想惹什么麻烦
I dont want any trouble.

14:52.930 --> 14:54.170
蠢货 绝不允许
Asshole Never

14:54.450 --> 14:57.150
永远别在我的地盘随地大小便
Never use my floor as a bathroom

14:57.670 --> 15:00.430
我想他明白了
I think he gets the message.

15:03.870 --> 15:05.700
我们两个可以单挑
We could go you and me

15:05.770 --> 15:07.370
就在这里
right here.

15:11.070 --> 15:13.900
你真有胆识
You're a brave man,huh?

15:13.970 --> 15:17.270
有种
Brave man.

15:18.900 --> 15:20.870
你很幸运 我现在温和多了
You're lucky I've been meditating.

15:20.930 --> 15:23.630
换作以前 早一枪毙了你
Before,I couldn't take my finger off the trigger,but now

15:23.700 --> 15:26.300
但我现在懂得了控制情绪
now I have mind control.

15:26.370 --> 15:29.370
完全的控制
Complete control.

15:29.430 --> 15:30.730
思想
Mind

15:30.800 --> 15:32.570
身体
body

15:32.630 --> 15:33.870
还有灵魂
and soul.

15:36.770 --> 15:37.770
滚出去吧
Get out

15:38.830 --> 15:41.470
快滚
Get out

15:49.830 --> 15:51.270
浪费我们的时间
He's a waste of our time.

15:51.330 --> 15:55.070
谁能想象索纳出了这样的风云人物
Who would have thought a famous person in Sona.

15:55.130 --> 15:57.630
弱者总是延续弱势
Weak people rally around fame.

15:57.700 --> 15:59.100
他们祈祷上苍 他们对此深信不疑
They worship it. They're blinded by it.

15:59.170 --> 16:01.030
正如你所知
And as you can tell,there are many people

16:01.100 --> 16:02.730
这里还有很多弱者
of weak character behind these walls.

16:02.800 --> 16:04.670
没错 他们会跟随像这样的人
Yes,they will follow a man like this,

16:04.730 --> 16:07.500
他们会给他立碑纪念
and they will put him on a pedestal.

16:07.570 --> 16:12.830
他很有魅力 是吗 宝贝?
He has that charisma,right,mami?

16:12.900 --> 16:14.670
他可比不上你
He's no you.

16:14.730 --> 16:17.430
宝贝 你不用来迎合我
Ah,you don't have to pander me,mami.

16:17.500 --> 16:19.300
我可不是三岁小孩
Soy un hombre maduro.

16:19.370 --> 16:20.470
他很帅 不是吗?
He's good looking,right?

16:21.670 --> 16:24.970
没错 他是很帅
Si. He is good looking.

16:25.770 --> 16:28.170
他是这里最帅的 不是吗?
He's the best looking man in the prison,right?

16:28.230 --> 16:29.830
和你不能比
Not compared to you.

16:30.230 --> 16:31.830
宝贝 让我来告诉你
Let me tell you, mammi.

16:32.230 --> 16:33.830
谁知道呢
Who knows

16:35.230 --> 16:36.830
或许是吧
Maybe

16:37.230 --> 16:39.130
臭婊子 给我滚蛋
Pack up, whore.

16:39.230 --> 16:40.430
别让我再看到你
You are gone.

17:30.650 --> 17:32.520
莎拉
Sara

17:44.500 --> 17:45.570
莎拉 唐克瑞蒂是个美国人
Sara Tancredi she's an American.

17:45.640 --> 17:46.770
她失踪了
She's missing.

17:46.840 --> 17:48.900
我们没有她的任何消息
We don't have a report of anything like that.

17:48.970 --> 17:51.200
但如果有的话 给我电话 号码在背面
But if you do,you call me;the number's on the back.

17:51.270 --> 17:53.400
好的 先生
Okay,ser.

17:53.470 --> 17:55.400
有任何消息就打给我 好吗?
Anything,you call me,all right?

17:55.470 --> 17:56.400
会的
Will do.

17:56.470 --> 17:58.940
谢谢
Thank you.

18:08.770 --> 18:10.300
你哪弄来的鞋子?
Where'd you get shoes?

18:19.770 --> 18:21.860
该干活还钱付租金了
It's time to start earning your rent around here.

18:21.890 --> 18:22.910
这里不用租金的
There's no rent here.

18:22.940 --> 18:24.400
-这是监狱 -继续说啊
It's prison.Keep talking.

18:24.470 --> 18:26.000
要上去了
It's going up.

18:26.070 --> 18:27.570
给
Here.

18:27.640 --> 18:29.240
干活时间到了
Work time's started right now.

18:30.300 --> 18:32.500
哪?
Where?

18:33.770 --> 18:35.170
哦 不
Uh-uh. Hell no.

18:35.240 --> 18:36.400
绝对没门
Absolutely not.

18:38.740 --> 18:40.600
再敢放屁
One more word from you,

18:40.670 --> 18:42.170
我让你吃屎 明白没?
and I will drown you in here,you understand?

18:44.800 --> 18:46.570
快点 干活
Now,work.

18:46.640 --> 18:49.200
做完后拿去下水道烧掉
Burn it down in the sewers when you're done.

19:19.200 --> 19:22.170
有新人来了

19:22.300 --> 19:23.370
一个美国人

19:24.240 --> 19:25.300
还有别的事么?

19:25.400 --> 19:27.200
他有只假手

19:56.840 --> 19:59.440
斯科菲尔德 有人来看你了
Scofield,una visita

19:59.500 --> 20:01.570
斯科菲尔德 有人来看你了
Scofield,visita

20:08.340 --> 20:09.900
斯科菲尔德 先生
Ah,Mr. Scofield.

20:09.970 --> 20:10.940
埃利奥特 派克
Elliot Pike.

20:11.000 --> 20:12.000
找我什么事
What do you want?

20:12.070 --> 20:14.300
说实话 是来代表你的
Well,to be frank,to represent you.

20:14.370 --> 20:15.900
-你是律师? -算是吧
You're a lawyer? Of sorts.

20:15.970 --> 20:17.970
法院已经指派了律师给我
The court already appointed me a lawyer.

20:20.000 --> 20:24.440
那或许我可以用别的方法帮你
Then perhaps I can be of assistance in a different way.

20:24.500 --> 20:26.440
我有点怀疑
Somehow I doubt that.

20:26.500 --> 20:29.000
我的靠山可厉害者呢 斯科菲尔德先生
I got a lot of big guns behind me,Mr. Scofield,

20:29.070 --> 20:31.440
你或许会需要他们的
people you might like to have in your corner

20:31.500 --> 20:34.970
你是否该考虑下 越狱呢
should you ever decide,say to break out of here.

20:38.870 --> 20:40.070
你是谁?
Who are you?

20:40.140 --> 20:43.040
我们可以从各方面帮助你
We can assist you in every possible way

20:43.100 --> 20:44.840
一旦你能越过那道墙
once you get past that wall.

20:48.840 --> 20:51.270
像你这样一个身怀绝技的人
There's a reason a guy like you,

20:51.340 --> 20:53.500
被关到这是有原因的 知道么
with your skill set,was put in here,you know.

20:55.740 --> 20:58.300
谈话到此为止
This conversation's over.

20:58.370 --> 21:00.170
斯科菲尔德 你得听听我说的
You ought to hear what I have to say,Scofield.

21:00.240 --> 21:02.040
我们想让事情简单点
We're trying to do this the easy way.

21:34.100 --> 21:36.440
你他妈搞什么 敢动我东西?
What the hell are you doing taking my stash?

21:36.500 --> 21:38.440
说啊 小娘们
Cough it up,you little bitch.

21:38.500 --> 21:40.270
-我没拿 -东西在哪?
I didn't do it. Where is it?

21:40.340 --> 21:42.140
-在哪? -不是我
Where is it? It wasn't me.

21:48.470 --> 21:51.170
你懂私自斗殴的规矩吧
You know the rules about extra-curricular fights

21:51.240 --> 21:53.240
这里可行不通
It doesn't happen here.

21:53.300 --> 21:55.270
他拿走了属于我的东西
He took something that belongs to me.

21:55.340 --> 21:56.340
他不大正常
He's out of his mind.

21:56.400 --> 21:59.600
这事很容易弄明白
Well,it seems pretty easy to get to the bottom of this

21:59.670 --> 22:00.200
搜他的身
check him.

22:06.970 --> 22:09.000
检查他的地方
Check his area.

22:19.300 --> 22:21.270
真见鬼
That's bull.

22:24.070 --> 22:25.140
你们都是
You're both

22:25.200 --> 22:27.770
贱人
scumbags.

22:32.340 --> 22:33.440
伙计 你和我
You and me,man.

22:33.500 --> 22:34.640
我们还没完呢
We're not done here.

22:40.070 --> 22:41.070
你见过这个女的没有
You haven't seen her?

22:41.070 --> 22:42.800
有长得相似的入住过吗
No one like this has checked in?

22:42.840 --> 22:44.040
先生 抱歉没有见过
No Sir.

22:44.440 --> 22:45.440
你真的确定吗
You're absolutely sure?

22:47.540 --> 22:49.600
谢谢
Thanks.

22:50.800 --> 22:51.970
是我
Yeah.

22:52.040 --> 22:54.640
布鲁斯先生 我是伊萨斯队长
Mr. Burrows. Captain Itzuris

22:54.700 --> 22:56.000
正在治安官的办公室里
at the constable's office.

22:56.070 --> 22:59.670
我们找到了一个美国女人
We found an American woman

22:59.740 --> 23:02.040
符合你对你朋友唐克瑞蒂小姐的描述
matching the description of your friend,Ms. Tancredi.

23:02.100 --> 23:04.100
在哪
Where?

23:04.170 --> 23:06.140
停尸房
At the morgue.

23:18.800 --> 23:20.200
他说的什么
What's he saying?

23:20.270 --> 23:21.600
我们不能吃这些
That we can't eat.

23:21.670 --> 23:23.100
那我们应该吃什么
What are we supposed to eat?

23:23.170 --> 23:29.100
求你了 来这一周 我都没进过食
Please. I haven't eaten in the week since i have been here..

23:38.640 --> 23:41.070
他们想要我们像狗一样的讨食
They expect us to forage,like dogs.

23:41.140 --> 23:43.570
我会死的 怎么都是死
I'll die.I will literally die.

23:49.740 --> 23:51.440
伙计 那就死好了
Hang in there,man.

24:23.940 --> 24:26.770
自娱自乐吧 帅哥
Playing by yourself.Same old Pretty.

24:26.840 --> 24:29.270
就是不大合群啊 对吧
Just not good at making friends,are you?

24:29.340 --> 24:31.070
我们之间没什么好说的
We got nothing to say to each other.

24:31.140 --> 24:32.540
换个角度来说
On another note,

24:32.600 --> 24:34.640
如果这是一部由政府导演的大片
on a big picture note,them big government types

24:34.700 --> 24:35.700
把我陷害得这么惨
that shook me down so hard,

24:35.700 --> 24:36.600
为什么他们要把你搞到这里来
why is it they wanted you here?

24:36.670 --> 24:38.240
索纳监狱就是他们的兴趣所在?
Was it Sona they was interested in?

24:38.300 --> 24:39.600
我就是这么想的
That's what I'm thinking.

24:39.670 --> 24:42.070
想让我到这个烂乡下地方来把你搅晕
Want me to get you down here,up in this very county.

24:42.140 --> 24:43.900
你是怎么认为的?
What do you think it is,huh?

24:43.970 --> 24:45.100
你认为真有人会对索纳监狱有兴趣?
You think it's Sona?

24:45.170 --> 24:47.240
谁会对这种破烂地方有兴趣?
Who'd be interested in a dump like this?

24:47.300 --> 24:50.570
有人逃跑
Runner Runner

25:15.970 --> 25:18.240
不 不
No No

26:06.800 --> 26:07.800
谢谢您通知我
Thanks for getting back to me.

26:08.060 --> 26:09.200
不用谢
No problem.

26:09.260 --> 26:11.530
尸体今天上午被钓出池塘
The body was fished out of the pond

26:11.600 --> 26:13.560
-今早发现的第一件 -在哪里发现的?
-first thing this morning. -Where?

26:13.630 --> 26:16.200
卡雷 瑟森塔赛思
Calle Sesenta-Seis.

26:16.260 --> 26:17.960
就在阿凡尼达 科隆西边
Just west of Avenida Colon.

26:21.030 --> 26:23.030
先生?
Sir?

26:23.100 --> 26:25.230
那是我最后一次看见她的地方
That's the last place I saw her.

26:41.830 --> 26:43.730
这不是她
It's not her.

26:45.260 --> 26:47.200
这不是她
It's not her.

27:01.130 --> 27:03.430
有人控告你
Someone's thrown the glove down on you.

27:03.500 --> 27:04.860
还是很严重的事情呢 是吧?
The gauntlet,right?

27:04.930 --> 27:07.000
是啊 只是我们都知道我没拿那些药
Yeah,except we both know I didn't take those drugs.

27:07.060 --> 27:08.760
我不是法官
I'm not the judge.

27:08.830 --> 27:10.800
我不处理这里的上诉
I don't deal in the claims people make.

27:10.860 --> 27:12.360
我只确保这里得按照规则运作
I just make sure the rules are followed.

27:12.430 --> 27:13.700
规则说一切冤屈的处理方法
And the rules say all grievances are dealt with

27:13.760 --> 27:16.700
都是2个人到圈里决斗
two men in a ring,a fight.

27:16.760 --> 27:19.700
我明天就离开了 没有必要这样
I'll be leaving tomorrow,so that won't be necessary.

27:19.760 --> 27:21.800
也许对你来说没有必要
It may not be necessary to you,

27:21.860 --> 27:23.130
但是对我来说很必要
but it is to me.

27:23.200 --> 27:26.130
我有职责维护这里的秩序
I have a duty to maintain order here

27:26.200 --> 27:28.530
用一个铁定的合法体制来确保
an ironclad legal system that assures that

27:28.600 --> 27:30.860
没人能自作主张处理他们的矛盾
no one goes independent with their grievances,

27:30.930 --> 27:32.860
那可是其他监狱里常有的事
as is so often the case in other prisons.

27:32.930 --> 27:33.930
在这里
Here,

27:34.000 --> 27:35.060
存在着一个体制
there is a system,

27:35.130 --> 27:37.300
这个体制就代表了秩序
and that system means order.

27:37.360 --> 27:39.060
所以不管你是否赞同
So whether you agree with it or not

27:39.130 --> 27:41.100
都和我没有关系
does not matter to me.

27:41.160 --> 27:42.830
我的议程比你的更重要
There's a larger agenda than yours.

27:47.260 --> 27:49.030
如果我拒绝会怎么样?
What happens if I refuse?

27:50.200 --> 27:53.400
我们会去找你
We'll come for you.

27:53.460 --> 27:55.900
我能保证你会得到一个
And I can guarantee you that is an outcome

27:55.960 --> 27:58.400
你不喜欢的结局
that you will not like.

27:58.460 --> 28:00.000
告诉我
Tell me something

28:00.060 --> 28:01.700
你总是用计来使人决斗吗?
do you always set up your fights?

28:01.760 --> 28:04.730
我和那一点关系都没有
I had nothing to do with it.

28:04.800 --> 28:06.830
整个监狱和我有冲突的人
And yet the only one in this whole prison

28:06.900 --> 28:09.000
至今只有你
who has a problem with me is you.

28:09.060 --> 28:12.230
我会很乐意见到巨星陨落
I'd be glad to see you go down superstar

28:25.330 --> 28:26.500
继续 继续做
Go on,keep going.

28:26.560 --> 28:28.800
在角落里把它烧了
You burn it around the corner.

28:52.560 --> 28:54.530
伙计
Buddy.

29:07.960 --> 29:09.560
可以帮我一个忙吗
Think you can do me a favor?

29:09.630 --> 29:11.700
休想
Bite me.

29:11.760 --> 29:13.830
我能给你吃的
I can feed you.

29:15.260 --> 29:17.800
几周前 我和你一样的处境
A few weeks ago,I was in your shoes.

29:17.860 --> 29:19.930
好几天没有东西吃
Didn't get any food for days.

29:20.000 --> 29:21.360
他们想让我死
They'd have let me die,

29:21.430 --> 29:22.860
就像他们想让你死一样
just like they're gonna let you die.

29:22.930 --> 29:24.460
回到给我吃的那个话题
Get back to the"feed me"part.

29:29.360 --> 29:31.130
鸡肉
Chicken.

29:31.200 --> 29:32.660
伙计 你哪里来的鸡肉
Man,where'd you get chicken?

29:34.200 --> 29:35.800
那不是鸡肉
That's not chicken.

29:40.900 --> 29:43.460
-还要再来点吗 -要
-Want some more? -Yeah.

29:43.530 --> 29:46.230
那你要帮我跑个腿
Then you're gonna have to run an errand for me.

29:46.300 --> 29:48.600
跑什么腿
What kind of errand?

29:58.200 --> 30:00.660
-爸爸 是我 -LJ
-Dad? It's me. -LJ.

30:00.730 --> 30:01.760
你在哪里
Where are you?

30:01.830 --> 30:03.200
我在巴拿马
I'm in Panama.

30:03.260 --> 30:05.460
什么
What?

30:05.530 --> 30:06.830
你
How

30:06.900 --> 30:08.360
你怎么得到这个号码的
How'd you get this number?

30:08.430 --> 30:09.660
我碰到莎拉
Well,I ran into Sara.

30:09.730 --> 30:11.300
她从领事馆得到你的号码
She got your number from the consulate.

30:11.360 --> 30:13.160
爸爸 我得挂了
Dad,I'm cutting out.

30:13.230 --> 30:14.900
LJ 我听不清楚
LJ,I can't hear you,man.

30:14.960 --> 30:16.530
爸爸 照我说的做
Dad,do this.

30:16.600 --> 30:19.030
和我们在加菲 普莱斯大厦见面
Meet us at the restaurant in the Garfield Price building

30:19.100 --> 30:20.300
在顶楼的餐馆
at the top.

30:20.360 --> 30:21.500
加菲什么
Garfield what?

30:21.560 --> 30:24.460
8点半
8:30

30:36.760 --> 30:39.230
决斗时间
Time to fight,blanco

30:45.800 --> 30:49.230
希望你没事
Best to make your peace with God.

30:51.730 --> 30:53.600
都安排好了?
all right?

30:53.700 --> 30:54.100
当然
Come on

30:54.200 --> 30:54.700
10对1
Ten to one.

30:54.900 --> 30:56.100
没人喜欢那美国佬
No one wants the American.

30:56.260 --> 30:57.900
什么?居然要10对1
What? Even at 10-1?

30:57.960 --> 31:00.060
所以他必须要投靠我们
There's a reason he chose World.

31:00.130 --> 31:02.660
已经连续死了6个了
Six consecutive life terms,okay?

31:09.130 --> 31:10.660
擦干净
Clean it up.

31:15.160 --> 31:16.600
我只是开个玩笑
I'm just kidding,man.

31:16.660 --> 31:20.000
放心吧
Tranquilo

31:25.330 --> 31:27.860
当然啦 因为您
Surely,it's beneath a man of your status

31:27.930 --> 31:29.100
在这正是把握全局
to be walking around like that

31:29.160 --> 31:30.860
的核心人物
all sticky-like.

31:30.930 --> 31:32.460
放了他
Leave him.

31:32.530 --> 31:33.960
你什么意思
What do you propose?

31:34.030 --> 31:36.800
帮您擦鞋
Ablution.

31:38.830 --> 31:42.160
为了投靠您的门下
A humble sign of friendship from a stranger

31:42.230 --> 31:44.730
以表达我最诚挚的善意
who's come into your house.

31:52.560 --> 31:54.000
哦 对不起
Sorry about that.

31:54.060 --> 31:57.230
我只是个废人
Just half a man down here.

31:59.230 --> 32:01.460
你叫什么?
What's your name,

32:01.530 --> 32:06.530
就叫我"朋友"好了
You can just call me"friend."

32:15.760 --> 32:17.760
对着膝关节就是一脚
Go for the kneecap.

32:19.060 --> 32:21.860
恩 就是你想的那样
You,uh you hit it

32:21.930 --> 32:23.300
直接踹上去 膝关节就断了
straight on,it'll buckle,

32:23.360 --> 32:26.130
你就能把那家伙彻底放倒
and you'll take the guy out of commission.

32:26.200 --> 32:28.700
使用诡计 这就是你的伎俩?
Fighting dirty? That's your secret?

32:28.760 --> 32:31.060
这世界上没什么光明正大的事
I didn't think there was any such thing as clean

32:31.130 --> 32:33.700
尤其是在这
in a place like this.

32:33.760 --> 32:36.230
阿历克斯 我很意外
You know,I'm surprised,Alex.

32:36.300 --> 32:38.200
没想到你还会关心人
It almost sounds like you care.

32:38.260 --> 32:41.300
你可是我离开这鬼地方的关键
You're my get-out-of-jail-free card.

32:42.860 --> 32:44.700
要活着
Just survive.

32:47.100 --> 32:48.900
记得踹膝盖 要用尽力气
Kneecap,really hard.

33:29.000 --> 33:30.600
祝你好运
Good luck,man.

33:59.660 --> 34:01.360
上帝保佑你
God bless,man.

34:11.430 --> 34:15.360
两只狗之间有争执
We got a disagreement between two dogs

34:15.430 --> 34:17.800
一个是瘾君子 另一个是扒手
a drug addict and a thief.

34:17.860 --> 34:20.360
两个我都不能饶恕
And I condone neither.

34:20.430 --> 34:22.430
我已经金盘洗手了
And I wash my hands of both of them.

34:22.500 --> 34:25.660
但是我们是有规矩的
But they have an issue,and we have rules.

34:25.730 --> 34:29.000
没有规矩 我们就和野蛮没两样
And without rules,we're nothing but savages.

34:29.060 --> 34:31.430
所以 我们要尊重规矩
Therefore,with proper respect for the rules,

34:31.500 --> 34:34.460
这次的决斗只有一个规定
this fight is engaged with only one rule

34:34.530 --> 34:36.460
不能用武器
no weapons.

34:36.530 --> 34:38.430
单挑
Only man versus man,

34:38.500 --> 34:41.260
不能借助物品和障碍
without augmentation or handicap.

34:42.360 --> 34:43.830
要说的都说完了
I'm done talking.

34:54.960 --> 34:56.630
我不会打的
I'm not going to fight

35:30.200 --> 35:34.060
你还没明白规矩 朋友
I don't think you understand the rules,friend.

35:34.130 --> 35:35.960
只有活着的人才能走出去
Only one man comes out alive.

36:30.960 --> 36:36.000
不能用武器 规矩不能坏 记得吗?
Rules are rules. Remember?

36:37.300 --> 36:39.140
如果我们没规矩
If we don't have them

36:39.200 --> 36:41.370
我们就是野蛮人
we're savages.

37:05.840 --> 37:07.340
对不起
Oh,excuse me.

37:07.400 --> 37:08.900
你没有穿外套
You have no jacket.

37:08.970 --> 37:10.640
我只是过来等下人 通融一下
Come on,man. I'm just meeting someone. Give me a break.

37:10.700 --> 37:12.700
这是个高级场所
Well,this is a nice place.

37:12.770 --> 37:14.100
要求要穿外套
It requires jackets.

37:14.170 --> 37:14.900
我没有
Well,I don't

37:14.970 --> 37:15.970
外套
have a jacket.

37:16.040 --> 37:17.270
必须要穿外套
It requires jackets.

37:18.970 --> 37:20.100
好
Fine.

37:28.840 --> 37:30.370
麻烦你
Excuse me.

37:30.440 --> 37:32.140
你会讲英语吗?
You speak English?

37:32.200 --> 37:34.540
那你认识美元的吧?
How about American?

37:49.400 --> 37:51.970
请给我一杯水
Can I grab a water,please?

37:52.040 --> 37:53.370
你大老远来巴拿马
Please tell me you didn't come

37:53.440 --> 37:55.600
不是只为了喝杯水吧
all the way to Panama for the water.

37:57.340 --> 38:00.140
为了家庭
Family.

38:01.670 --> 38:04.670
夹克挺不错的 萨杰奥
That's a nice jacket,Sergio.

38:04.740 --> 38:07.970
说来话长了
It's a long story.

38:08.040 --> 38:10.140
谢谢
Thank you.

38:10.200 --> 38:12.270
你在等人吧?
You're waiting for someone,huh?

38:12.340 --> 38:13.470
嗯
Uh-huh.

38:13.540 --> 38:14.600
我早该知道
I should have known.

38:14.670 --> 38:16.640
长相不错的男人总是先被人挑走了
Good-looking ones are always taken.

38:20.640 --> 38:22.640
你的脸怎么了?
What happened to your face?

38:22.700 --> 38:24.140
猫抓的
A cat.

38:24.200 --> 38:26.300
猫 一定是好大的猫
Cat. It's a big cat.

38:26.370 --> 38:28.670
你不要提问题
You push anything too far into a corner,

38:28.740 --> 38:30.340
太刨根问底了好吗
and the claws will come out.

38:32.540 --> 38:34.500
夫人 也许你总是选择的时机不对
Your timing's all wrong,lady.

38:34.570 --> 38:35.900
噢 得了吧 过来一起吧
Oh,come on. Hang out.

38:35.970 --> 38:40.440
我很愿意 只不过现在不行
I'd like to but it ain't the right time.

38:42.640 --> 38:45.300
林肯 的确时机不合适
Yes,it is,Lincoln.

38:49.070 --> 38:50.900
看起来我们有得聊了
We have a lot to discuss.

38:50.970 --> 38:52.670
特别是 关于你弟弟
Specifically,your brother.

38:57.140 --> 38:59.370
我强烈建议
I highly suggest

38:59.440 --> 39:01.900
你跟他聊聊
you talk to him.

39:23.440 --> 39:25.900
把里面的死尸带出来吧
The dead men inside Bring them out

39:27.440 --> 39:28.700
我想葬了他
I want to bury him

40:38.040 --> 40:39.540
他们会被葬在这
They will be buried here.

40:40.040 --> 40:42.540
除非他们家人出面 自己料理后事
Unless their family members step forward to make their own arrangements.

41:30.040 --> 41:31.540
转运我去另一个监狱的事情进行得怎么样?
How are we coming with the transfer?

41:34.340 --> 41:35.270
有一伙人
There are some people

41:35.340 --> 41:37.240
希望你可以帮他们把里面的某个人弄出去
that want you ask someone out of there.

41:37.250 --> 41:38.570
我知道
Yeah,I know.

41:38.580 --> 41:40.070
他们有跟我接触过
Some guy already approached me.

41:40.340 --> 41:41.340
我拒绝了他们
I said,"No,thank you."

41:42.010 --> 41:42.840
你必须待在里面
You got to stay.

41:44.110 --> 41:45.440
你说什么?
What are you talking about?

41:46.510 --> 41:47.770
那个人的名字是詹姆斯 韦斯勒
His name's James Whistler

41:48.040 --> 41:50.640
不行 不行 林肯 我不想再这么做了
No,no,no,no,Linc,I can't do that again.

41:50.910 --> 41:52.640
迈克
Michael.

41:55.910 --> 41:57.840
说话
Talk.

41:58.110 --> 42:00.240
爸爸
Dad.

42:00.640 --> 42:02.470
爸爸 对不起
Dad,I'm so sorry.

42:02.740 --> 42:03.540
他们抓住了我和莎拉
They got me and Sara.

42:05.140 --> 42:07.510
照他们的吩咐去做好吗
Please,do what they want.

42:07.770 --> 42:09.140
爸爸 求你了
Dad,please.

42:09.410 --> 42:12.410
你有一周的时间
You got a week

42:12.670 --> 42:13.810
找到那个韦斯勒
to find this Whistler guy.

42:14.070 --> 42:16.170
然后想办法把他弄出来
Get him out of there.

42:16.440 --> 42:17.370
否则 他们
Otherwise,they,uh

42:17.640 --> 42:19.340
莎拉和LJ 他们就死定了
Sara and LJ they both die.
